<p>The navigation bar pattern displays a horizontal navigation menu for pages related to the current page.</p>

<h3>Rules for the navigation bar</h3>

<ul>
    <li>Must be present on all webpages, apart from long-form stories.</li>
    <li>Must come below the category header and above the main body of the page.</li>
    <li>Must not contain any dropdown menus.</li>
    <li>Must only contain links to other webpages or web applications.</li>
    <li>Should not contain more than eight links.</li>
</ul>

